      },
      {
        icon: 'tabler:database-off',
        title: 'Zero database manipulation',
        description: 'No direct ODBC connections, no SQL writes to SAP B1 tables. Every transaction flows through the official Service Layer — keeping the ERP pristine and auditable.',
      },
      {
        icon: 'tabler:coin-off',
        title: 'Lower total cost of ownership',
        description: 'Eliminate add-on license costs, specialist consultant dependency, and upgrade rework. The Clean Core model reduces long-term SAP B1 maintenance overhead significantly.',
